# System Architecture: AI-Powered Appraisal System

## Architecture Overview

### Architecture Style Decision

| Decision | Selection | Rationale |
|----------|-----------|-----------|
| **Primary Style** | Modular Monolith | Simplifies initial deployment, reduces network complexity, allows future extraction to microservices |
| **Deployment** | Cloud-Native (AWS/Azure/GCP) | Auto-scaling, managed services, high availability |
| **Communication** | Synchronous: REST + Async: Message Queue | REST for user-facing APIs, message queue for background jobs |

