## Major Components

### 1. Frontend Layer

| Component | Technology | Purpose |
|-----------|------------|---------|
| **React SPA** | React 18 + TypeScript | Employee, Manager, HR dashboards |
| **State Management** | TanStack Query + Zustand | Server state caching, UI state |
| **UI Components** | shadcn/ui + Tailwind CSS | Accessible, enterprise-ready components |
| **Real-time** | WebSocket (Socket.io/WS) | Live sync notifications |

### 2. Backend Modules (Modular Monolith)

| Module | Responsibility | Key APIs |
|--------|----------------|----------|
| **API Gateway** | Auth, rate limiting, request routing | `/api/v1/*` |
| **Auth Module** | User authentication, JWT, RBAC | `/api/auth/*` |
| **Employee Module** | Self-service, context, achievements | `/api/employee/*` |
| **Manager Module** | Team management, appraisals, AI drafts | `/api/manager/*` |
| **HR Module** | Calibration, audit, compliance | `/api/hr/*` |
| **Leader Module** | Org summaries, promotions | `/api/leader/*` |
| **Admin Module** | Integrations, config, cycles | `/api/admin/*` |
| **AI Module** | Draft generation, bias detection, suggestions | Internal gRPC |
| **Analytics Module** | Aggregations, trending, reporting | Internal |

### 3. Shared Services

| Service | Purpose | Implementation |
|---------|---------|----------------|
| **Audit Logger** | Record all AI/manager actions | Async write to PostgreSQL + Elasticsearch |
| **Notification Service** | Email, in-app, webhook alerts | Redis queue + SMTP/WebSocket |
| **Calibration Service** | Bias detection, outlier flagging | Scheduled cron + AI evaluation |
| **Export Service** | CSV/PDF report generation | Background job + S3 |
| **Search Service** | Full-text search across entities | Elasticsearch |

